postings.body:
This is a beautiful, large apartment available within a townhouse located about a 5-minute walk from Central Square. The apartment has 4 bedrooms and 2 are available to move in on September 1st.
The apartment is two levels, first floor and garden level. There is one very large bedroom located on the first floor and two large bedrooms located downstairs. On each floor, there is a large living room with a very open feel. There are 2.5 bathrooms (1.5 upstairs, 1 downstairs) and a washer/dryer unit on the garden level. The modern kitchen is a great size, with an island that contains the stove/oven, as well as a dishwasher and large refrigerator/freezer. The apartment also has central air conditioning, central heat, a gas fire place, and hardwood floors throughout.
The apartment location is ideal as it is a 5 minute walk to Central Square (with access to the Red Line and multiple bus routes) and there is even a bus route that stops right near the apartment (#47 bus). There is a park located nearby along with a Hubway station for renting bikes, as well as tons off-street parking available (I have never once had an issue finding a spot within a block, and usually can park right out front).
I am a working professional in the downtown Boston area and have lived in this apartment for the past 2 years. I am clean, quiet, fun, and a good roommate overall and am looking for the same in 2 people to move in. Please contact me via Craigslist email and I`ll be happy to give you more information or show the apartment.
